          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Most window installation projects in Annapolis take just one to two days for an average-sized home. Our crews work efficiently to ensure every window is properly insulated and sealed for Mid-Atlantic weather conditions, minimizing disruption to your household."
