            "text": "Most residential window replacement projects in Annapolis do not require a building permit. However, homes in the Annapolis Historic District may be subject to additional local review. Capitol Improvements verifies local permit requirements for your specific Annapolis property before any work begins."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "What type of replacement windows are best for waterfront homes near the Chesapeake Bay in Annapolis?",
