            "text": "For Bay-front and Severn River properties in Annapolis, we recommend reinforced vinyl or composite-frame windows with stainless steel hardware and low-E coastal glass to resist salt air corrosion and high winds. These options deliver long-term durability without sacrificing energy efficiency or aesthetics."
